Doane et al. v. Field et al. C. M. Randall, for the appellants. Wharton, Benjamin and Micou, for the intervenors. No counsel appeared for the defendants.

THIS appeal brought up from the Commercial Court of New Orleans, Watts, J., involved the same questions as the case of Fetter and others, against the same defendants, ante p. 80, and was decided in the same way, for the reasons given in the opinion pronounced in that case.
